members.name: BluetoothAdvertisingData.appearance
members.description: Returns one of the values defined by the org.bluetooth.characteristic.gap.appearance characteristic.

members.name: BluetoothAdvertisingData.txPower
members.description: Returns the transmission power at which the device is broadcasting, measured in dBm. This is used to compute the path loss as this.txPower - this.rssi.

members.name: BluetoothAdvertisingData.rssi
members.description: Returns the power at which the device’s packets are being received, measured in dBm. This is used to compute the path loss as this.txPower - this.rssi.

members.name: BluetoothAdvertisingData.manufacturerData
members.description: Returns a map that relates Company Identifier Codes to ArrayBuffers.

members.name: BluetoothAdvertisingData.serviceData
members.description: Returns a map that relates UUIDs to ArrayBuffers.
